WEBVTT

00:02:12.760 --> 00:02:13.720
This Lu Wei,

00:02:14.040 --> 00:02:14.200
KTV colleague.

00:02:14.200 --> 00:02:15.960
we interrogated him during

00:02:15.960 --> 00:02:16.840
Qiao Sisi's car accident case.

00:02:16.840 --> 00:02:17.360
KTV colleague.

00:02:17.360 --> 00:02:18.200
So,

00:02:19.720 --> 00:02:21.520
was he hiding something from us?

00:02:23.600 --> 00:02:24.460
Go check it out.

00:02:24.520 --> 00:02:25.780
Pan Shuping and Lu Wei.

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:27.160
Confirm if

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:28.640
they have any connections

00:02:28.640 --> 00:02:29.800
to Huguang KTV

00:02:29.800 --> 00:02:31.329
and the serial murder case.

00:02:44.320 --> 00:02:44.760
Wait,

00:02:45.520 --> 00:02:46.450
why are you back?

00:02:47.760 --> 00:02:48.600
It's just tailing someone.

00:02:48.600 --> 00:02:50.460
Lin Xiao and the others are there.

00:02:51.280 --> 00:02:52.540
You're unbelievable.

00:02:52.560 --> 00:02:54.620
You assigned your own task to others.

00:02:55.079 --> 00:02:55.720
I came to see

00:02:55.720 --> 00:02:57.560
if there's anything I can do here.

00:02:57.560 --> 00:03:00.020
Why don't you be the captain and take charge?

00:03:01.840 --> 00:03:02.970
Where are you going?

00:03:09.440 --> 00:03:10.300
Have you eaten?

00:03:14.760 --> 00:03:15.420
At the gate,

00:03:15.440 --> 00:03:16.360
Old Han's place.

00:03:16.360 --> 00:03:17.120
Put it on my tab.

00:03:17.120 --> 00:03:17.600
Go.

00:03:20.200 --> 00:03:20.680
Master.

00:03:20.720 --> 00:03:22.040
I knew you

00:03:22.240 --> 00:03:22.920
scold me on the outside,

00:03:22.920 --> 00:03:24.320
but love me on the inside.

00:03:25.280 --> 00:03:27.440
I told you to pack it for the guys.

00:03:27.720 --> 00:03:28.560
As for you,

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:29.680
learn your lesson.

00:03:29.680 --> 00:03:30.610
Don't eat today.

00:03:30.960 --> 00:03:33.160
Leaving your post without permission.

00:03:33.280 --> 00:03:34.520
Did you forget what I told you

00:03:34.520 --> 00:03:35.440
on the first day we met?

00:03:35.440 --> 00:03:36.320
The first lesson for a police officer is

00:03:36.320 --> 00:03:37.440
to obey orders.

00:03:37.680 --> 00:03:39.200
Follow commands.

00:03:39.640 --> 00:03:40.240
I will

00:03:40.680 --> 00:03:42.010
reflect deeply on this.

00:04:10.200 --> 00:04:11.860
Hello, what do you need to buy?

00:04:12.160 --> 00:04:13.020
Hello, Miss Li.

00:04:14.640 --> 00:04:15.440
There's something

00:04:15.440 --> 00:04:16.769
we need to ask you about.

00:04:22.200 --> 00:04:23.640
From 2003 to 2005,

00:04:23.640 --> 00:04:24.120
you worked

00:04:24.120 --> 00:04:25.120
at Huguang KTV.

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:26.400
The boss at that time

00:04:26.400 --> 00:04:27.260
was Zhang Biao.

00:04:27.560 --> 00:04:28.480
He valued you

00:04:28.600 --> 00:04:29.200
and put you in charge

00:04:29.200 --> 00:04:30.080
of VIP clients.

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:31.200
You met

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:33.320
a friend there

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:35.530
named Guan Jing.

00:04:36.240 --> 00:04:36.680
Yes,

00:04:36.840 --> 00:04:38.770
we had a pretty good relationship.

00:04:39.080 --> 00:04:40.000
On August 9, 2005,

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:41.080
you reported

00:04:41.120 --> 00:04:42.880
that Guan Jing went missing.

00:04:43.520 --> 00:04:44.320
On August 12,

00:04:44.680 --> 00:04:45.940
you withdrew the case,

00:04:45.960 --> 00:04:47.159
saying she was found.

00:04:47.240 --> 00:04:47.720
Yes,

00:04:48.200 --> 00:04:48.760
but

00:04:48.840 --> 00:04:50.040
she was already dead.

00:04:50.360 --> 00:04:52.080
Her tomb is at Xifeng Mountain.

00:04:52.080 --> 00:04:52.840
Dead?

00:04:54.040 --> 00:04:54.900
How did she die?

00:04:55.840 --> 00:04:57.560
She had congenital heart disease.

00:04:57.560 --> 00:04:58.480
Because of this,

00:04:58.480 --> 00:05:00.000
she came out to work and make money

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:01.130
in order to survive.

00:05:03.240 --> 00:05:04.360
When she passed away,

00:05:04.360 --> 00:05:06.290
I also tried to contact her family.

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:08.920
They felt the funeral would cost money,

00:05:08.960 --> 00:05:10.690
so no one came to claim her body.

00:05:10.880 --> 00:05:12.740
I took care of everything for her.

00:05:13.920 --> 00:05:15.360
But when you withdrew the case,

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:16.520
you said she

00:05:16.680 --> 00:05:18.760
was sent to the hospital for a sudden illness.

00:05:18.760 --> 00:05:19.690
Which hospital?

00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:22.460
It was like this, officer.

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:25.660
At that time, Zhang Biao and Liu Jiang called me.

00:05:26.120 --> 00:05:27.580
Guan Jing had an accident.

00:05:27.880 --> 00:05:29.240
So when I saw her again,

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:31.240
she was already at the funeral home.

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:32.200
Liu Jiang,

00:05:32.320 --> 00:05:32.800
right?

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:33.480
Yes.

00:05:33.680 --> 00:05:35.680
Liu Jiang handled the hospitalization.

00:05:35.680 --> 00:05:37.680
He has connections at the hospital.

00:05:39.320 --> 00:05:41.600
Did Guan Jing have any friends while she was alive?

00:05:41.600 --> 00:05:42.330
A boyfriend?

00:05:45.120 --> 00:05:46.120
I'm not very sure.

00:05:47.560 --> 00:05:48.640
The medical records say

00:05:48.640 --> 00:05:49.000
her

00:05:49.000 --> 00:05:49.920
heart disease

00:05:49.920 --> 00:05:50.920
was stable.

00:05:51.400 --> 00:05:52.159
How could she

00:05:52.159 --> 00:05:53.760
die of a sudden heart attack?

00:05:55.200 --> 00:05:56.330
It's heart disease.

00:05:56.400 --> 00:05:57.260
You never know.

00:05:57.800 --> 00:05:58.680
It's fate.

00:06:07.360 --> 00:06:08.360
In January 2005,

00:06:09.320 --> 00:06:09.840
you picked up something

00:06:09.840 --> 00:06:12.480
at the mailroom of the City Photography Association.

00:06:12.480 --> 00:06:13.360
Do you remember?

00:06:13.360 --> 00:06:14.160
I remember.

00:06:15.440 --> 00:06:16.680
I helped

00:06:16.680 --> 00:06:18.440
Zhang Biao pick up a camera.

00:06:25.640 --> 00:06:26.300
Zhang Biao?

00:06:28.280 --> 00:06:28.800
Yes.

00:06:40.840 --> 00:06:41.760
That camera

00:06:41.760 --> 00:06:42.720
took a picture.

00:06:42.920 --> 00:06:43.520
Could you please

00:06:43.520 --> 00:06:44.320
take a look?

00:06:44.840 --> 00:06:46.500
Is the girl on the coffee table

00:06:47.040 --> 00:06:47.920
Guan Jing?

00:06:53.240 --> 00:06:54.880
Can I take a closer look?

00:07:03.920 --> 00:07:04.520
Yes.

00:07:04.800 --> 00:07:05.440
It's her.

00:07:10.920 --> 00:07:13.320
The Traditional Chinese Medicine Hospital is in the development zone, 25 kilometers away.

00:07:13.320 --> 00:07:14.520
According to Li Ting,

00:07:14.600 --> 00:07:16.200
Guan Jing fell ill suddenly.

00:07:16.280 --> 00:07:18.740
They had to send her to the nearest hospital.

00:07:18.760 --> 00:07:19.320
Hello.

00:07:19.360 --> 00:07:22.820
Here is the copy of Guan Jing's medical records you requested.

00:07:31.000 --> 00:07:31.880
In August 2005,

00:07:32.200 --> 00:07:33.360
Guan Jing never came here.

00:07:33.360 --> 00:07:35.220
All the medical records are here.

00:07:41.520 --> 00:07:44.780
Guan Jing has multiple gynecological treatment records.

00:07:45.640 --> 00:07:47.080
Zhang had an abortion once.

00:07:47.080 --> 00:07:49.540
But during the timeframe Li Ting mentioned,

00:07:49.600 --> 00:07:51.800
the hospital has no record of her visit.

00:07:55.400 --> 00:07:56.330
Li Ting is lying.

00:07:57.760 --> 00:07:59.840
She first reported Guan Jing missing.

00:07:59.840 --> 00:08:01.300
Then something happened,

00:08:01.320 --> 00:08:03.520
so she decided to lie and drop the case.

00:08:07.200 --> 00:08:07.920
Guan Jing.

00:08:09.680 --> 00:08:10.680
Could it be because

00:08:10.680 --> 00:08:11.810
of her death itself?

00:08:12.120 --> 00:08:13.240
If so.

00:08:14.360 --> 00:08:15.160
The secret room.

00:08:15.160 --> 00:08:15.800
Li Ting.

00:08:15.840 --> 00:08:16.440
Guan Jing.

00:08:17.200 --> 00:08:18.530
They are all connected.

00:08:18.960 --> 00:08:19.720
And Li Ting

00:08:20.880 --> 00:08:23.080
is the key to unlocking all the secrets.

00:08:36.200 --> 00:08:37.530
They have already left.

00:08:39.240 --> 00:08:40.500
You told me what to say,

00:08:40.720 --> 00:08:42.450
and I said it exactly like that.

00:08:52.080 --> 00:08:53.410
These flowers are nice.

00:08:53.800 --> 00:08:54.600
They look

00:08:54.880 --> 00:08:55.610
quite fresh.

00:08:59.800 --> 00:09:01.260
Please wrap these flowers

00:09:02.560 --> 00:09:03.600
up for me.

00:09:04.600 --> 00:09:05.800
Wrap them to look like

00:09:06.240 --> 00:09:07.280
how you used to be,

00:09:08.120 --> 00:09:08.920
sweet,

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:10.040
beautiful,

00:09:10.640 --> 00:09:11.480
and tender.

00:09:14.320 --> 00:09:16.450
When will you give my things back to me?

00:09:18.360 --> 00:09:19.440
Your things?

00:09:20.440 --> 00:09:20.800
Hey.

00:09:21.240 --> 00:09:22.440
What things of yours?

00:09:24.440 --> 00:09:26.200
You promised me.

00:09:26.280 --> 00:09:28.120
As long as I did what you said,

00:09:28.120 --> 00:09:30.050
you would give my photos back to me.

00:09:36.000 --> 00:09:37.530
Just because you're in them

00:09:37.640 --> 00:09:39.240
doesn't mean they're yours.

00:09:39.560 --> 00:09:41.200
Those are works of art.

00:09:42.320 --> 00:09:44.040
My works of art.

00:09:44.360 --> 00:09:45.890
Do you even understand art?

00:09:50.800 --> 00:09:52.320
I just want back my...

00:09:52.320 --> 00:09:53.360
The way you are now,

00:09:53.360 --> 00:09:55.760
you'd pollute those works of art, you know?

00:10:00.120 --> 00:10:00.800
I'm sorry.

00:10:02.120 --> 00:10:04.780
I treated you like you were back in school again.

00:10:06.120 --> 00:10:07.720
It was better back in school.

00:10:09.120 --> 00:10:10.440
I remember back in school,

00:10:10.440 --> 00:10:12.200
you liked sandalwood perfume.

00:10:12.960 --> 00:10:15.360
The kind of person who likes this perfume is

00:10:15.680 --> 00:10:16.760
strong-willed,

00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:18.080
understanding,

00:10:18.440 --> 00:10:20.300
and most importantly, obedient.

00:10:20.360 --> 00:10:21.560
But now, you...

00:10:21.880 --> 00:10:24.210
Hanging around so many flowers every day,

00:10:24.240 --> 00:10:25.970
the scent is too overpowering.

00:10:26.240 --> 00:10:26.920
You,

00:10:27.880 --> 00:10:29.680
should just come back to school.

00:10:30.200 --> 00:10:31.400
Come back to me.

00:10:32.320 --> 00:10:34.160
Let me purify your mind

00:10:34.600 --> 00:10:36.000
and your body.

00:10:39.800 --> 00:10:41.200
I just want

00:10:42.280 --> 00:10:44.200
to live a normal life.

00:10:44.320 --> 00:10:45.080
Don't worry.

00:10:45.280 --> 00:10:46.680
Everything you've done,

00:10:46.680 --> 00:10:48.320
I won't tell anyone.

00:10:49.240 --> 00:10:49.600
I...

00:10:49.760 --> 00:10:51.520
I just want those photos.

00:10:52.280 --> 00:10:53.080
Please.

00:10:55.080 --> 00:10:56.200
Oh, Li Ting.

00:10:58.880 --> 00:11:01.140
You really aren't as obedient as before.

00:11:01.200 --> 00:11:02.040
Besides,

00:11:02.240 --> 00:11:03.400
what you just said

00:11:03.400 --> 00:11:04.680
is wrong.

00:11:04.920 --> 00:11:07.160
What do you mean 'the things I did'?

00:11:07.960 --> 00:11:08.840
Aren't they

00:11:09.320 --> 00:11:11.360
the things we did together?

00:11:12.360 --> 00:11:13.820
You need to remember this.

00:11:14.920 --> 00:11:15.920
Anything,

00:11:16.000 --> 00:11:17.400
can only be given by me.

00:11:19.840 --> 00:11:21.960
You have no right to ask me for it.

00:11:24.200 --> 00:11:24.930
Understand?

00:11:31.280 --> 00:11:31.960
Sigh.

00:11:34.000 --> 00:11:35.800
Even the most beautiful flowers

00:11:35.920 --> 00:11:37.080
will wither

00:11:37.520 --> 00:11:38.720
and fade.

00:11:40.480 --> 00:11:42.200
Wrap the flowers beautifully for me

00:11:42.200 --> 00:11:43.660
and send them to my office.

00:11:52.840 --> 00:11:53.520
Captain Sun.

00:11:53.520 --> 00:11:55.160
We found Pan Shuping's place.

00:11:55.160 --> 00:11:56.320
I texted you the address.

00:11:56.320 --> 00:11:56.680
Okay.

00:11:57.320 --> 00:11:59.050
Yan and I are heading there now.

00:12:03.400 --> 00:12:03.880
Yan.

00:12:04.200 --> 00:12:04.930
Captain Sun.

00:12:05.800 --> 00:12:06.860
The neighbors said

00:12:07.360 --> 00:12:08.320
there's been no activity at Pan Shuping's place

00:12:08.320 --> 00:12:09.440
for over ten days.

00:12:09.640 --> 00:12:10.170
The water

00:12:10.200 --> 00:12:10.760
and electricity meters

00:12:10.760 --> 00:12:11.640
have stopped running.

00:12:11.640 --> 00:12:12.970
The landlord is inside.

00:12:13.960 --> 00:12:15.420
Let's go in and take a look.

00:12:22.320 --> 00:12:24.450
About how long has she been renting it?

00:12:24.640 --> 00:12:26.100
She's been renting for...

00:12:26.640 --> 00:12:27.720
Three months ago,

00:12:27.960 --> 00:12:29.020
she just rented it.

00:12:29.960 --> 00:12:31.760
Did Pan Shuping come with Lu Wei,

00:12:31.760 --> 00:12:33.760
or did she rent your place by herself?

00:12:33.760 --> 00:12:36.020
She came alone when she rented the place.

00:12:36.720 --> 00:12:39.450
How much was the monthly rent for this place then?

00:12:39.720 --> 00:12:40.680
About 2,000.

00:12:43.080 --> 00:12:44.440
Do you still have the contract?

00:12:44.440 --> 00:12:45.120
I do.

00:12:45.120 --> 00:12:46.120
I'll get it for you.

00:12:46.120 --> 00:12:46.840
Okay.

00:15:03.400 --> 00:15:05.080
This should be the primary crime scene.

00:15:05.080 --> 00:15:05.880
The bathroom floor drain

00:15:05.880 --> 00:15:07.610
still smells of disinfectant.

00:15:07.640 --> 00:15:08.800
After the murder,

00:15:09.160 --> 00:15:10.290
the killer must have

00:15:10.680 --> 00:15:12.680
done some cleaning in the bathroom.

00:15:14.200 --> 00:15:16.840
The kitchen knife was probably taken by the killer.

00:15:16.840 --> 00:15:17.720
The bedding

00:15:17.760 --> 00:15:18.680
and the curtains

00:15:18.680 --> 00:15:19.680
are also missing.

00:15:19.880 --> 00:15:20.940
It's highly likely

00:15:20.960 --> 00:15:22.400
that during the murder,

00:15:22.400 --> 00:15:23.600
they got stained with blood

00:15:23.600 --> 00:15:24.120
or

00:15:24.720 --> 00:15:25.800
were used to wrap the body.

00:15:25.800 --> 00:15:27.060
The entire crime scene

00:15:27.680 --> 00:15:29.280
and the body disposal method

00:15:29.800 --> 00:15:32.000
are completely different from before.

00:15:32.680 --> 00:15:34.740
It's probably not the serial killer.

00:15:36.240 --> 00:15:37.700
I'll call forensics over.

00:15:48.560 --> 00:15:49.490
Hello, Mr. Wang.

00:15:49.560 --> 00:15:50.720
I've sent you Lu Wei's address.

00:15:50.720 --> 00:15:52.320
Get here as soon as possible.

00:15:55.240 --> 00:15:55.720
Okay.

00:16:07.880 --> 00:16:08.880
This is the place.

00:16:09.480 --> 00:16:10.410
Let's go inside.

00:16:15.760 --> 00:16:17.290
The door isn't even locked.

00:16:26.200 --> 00:16:27.060
Is anyone here?

00:16:30.840 --> 00:16:31.800
Disinfectant,

00:16:32.080 --> 00:16:33.120
cleaning agent,

00:16:33.160 --> 00:16:33.920
shovel,

00:16:33.960 --> 00:16:34.760
and saw blade.

00:16:40.960 --> 00:16:41.820
Is anyone here?

00:17:03.480 --> 00:17:04.210
Captain Sun.

00:17:20.640 --> 00:17:21.970
He arrived at 2:00 a.m.,

00:17:22.119 --> 00:17:23.960
which matches the estimated time of death

00:17:23.960 --> 00:17:25.619
given by the forensic doctor.

00:17:25.640 --> 00:17:28.480
I called the number on the business card several times on the way here,

00:17:28.480 --> 00:17:29.680
but it was turned off.

00:17:34.120 --> 00:17:34.760
Most likely,

00:17:34.760 --> 00:17:36.120
it was a crime of passion.

00:17:36.120 --> 00:17:37.650
He dumped the body and fled.

00:17:38.600 --> 00:17:39.130
Lin Xiao,

00:17:39.320 --> 00:17:40.760
go check this license plate.

00:17:40.760 --> 00:17:41.240
Han,

00:17:41.440 --> 00:17:42.680
contact the other departments.

00:17:42.680 --> 00:17:43.040
Okay.